ink":"https://www.ifanr.com/1655944?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-27 10:40:21","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f9f5c72b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_43438ea0","title":"何恺明团队新作 GeoPT，全新预训练范式让模型自学真实物理规律","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/382888.html","date":"2026-02-27 08:19:25","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_43438ea0.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_3ce9568f","title":"囤积你已知如何实现的东西 —— 智能体工程模式","link":"https://simonwillison.net/guides/agentic-engineering-patterns/hoard-things-you-know-how-to-do/#atom-everything","date":"2026-02-26 20:33:27","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3ce9568f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":6,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_35edc300","title":"CORPGEN 推动 AI 智能体处理真实工作","link":"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/corpgen-advances-ai-agents-for-real-work/","date":"2026-02-26 17:10:15","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_35edc300.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Microsoft Research Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_3308e250","title":"智谱 GLM-5 技术全公开！完全适配华为等国产芯片，美国网友酸了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/381712.html","date":"2026-02-23 05:19:44","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3308e250.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":21,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_03c4951e","title":"从“凭感觉测试”到持续评估：构建可靠的 AI 智能体","link":"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/developers-practitioners/from-vibe-checks-to-continuous-evaluation-engineering-reliable-ai-agents/","date":"2026-02-28 00:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文提供了一个全面的工程框架，旨在将 AI 智能体开发从主观的“凭感觉测试”转向严谨、自动化的持续评估（CE）工作流。","summary":"本文探讨了“凭感觉测试陷阱”——即开发者依赖手动、主观测试，导致无法捕捉概率性 AI 系统中的回归问题。文章倡导“持续评估”（CE），这是一种将传统软件工程的严谨性应用于 AI 智能体的学科。作者引入了双模式思维：“发现模式”用于创意探索，“防御模式”用于工业级可靠性。文章以多智能体“课程生成器”系统为例，详细介绍了基于 Agent2Agent (A2A) 协议的模块化架构。它将评估分为三个级别：基于确定性计算的指标、基于评分细则的 LLM-as-a-judge 评分，以及如 Vertex AI 的接地性（grounding）和安全性指标等托管自动评估器。最后，文章提供了并行推理和自定义工具轨迹评估的技术实现细节，以确保智能体能够正确且可预测地使用外部工具。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_03c4951e.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Google Cloud Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_e440d9a8","title":"Vercel 发布 React 最佳实践技能，包含 40 多条面向 AI 智能体的性能规则","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/vercel-react-best-practices/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-27 14:30:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Vercel 发布了一个包含 40 多条 React 和 Next.js 性能规则的开源仓库，专门为 AI 编程智能体格式化，旨在优化架构决策。","summary":"Vercel 全新的 “react-best-practices” 仓库将十多年的工程经验总结为 40 多条性能优化规则。与关注语法的传统 Linter 不同，该框架解决了诸如异步瀑布流和包体积优化等高层架构问题。它主要为 Cursor 和 Claude Code 等 AI 智能体设计，提供结构化的 AGENTS.md 文件和代码示例，引导 LLM 生成更高性能的代码。虽然社区对“氛围编程”（vibe coding）上下文环境的改善表示欢迎，但一些开发者对供应链安全以及 AI 理解复杂业务逻辑的能力表示担忧。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_e440d9a8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_a2add981","title":"结合架构即代码的安全性 API 连接平台","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/secure-connectivity-api/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-27 09:19:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a2add981.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":34,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_16ac06ee","title":"BestBlogs 周刊第 84 期：当工程师变成编排者","link":"https://ginonotes.com/posts/bestblogs-weekly-issue-84","date":"2026-02-27 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_